import { Caption, Heading, Paragraph } from "../../components/Text";

import Form from "../../components/Form";
import React from "react";
import Section from "../../components/Section";

export default () => (
	<React.Fragment>
		<Section>
			<Heading>Contact Us</Heading>
			<Paragraph>
				Got a question? Don't hesitate to get in touch with us using the
				contact form provided.
			</Paragraph>
		</Section>
		<Section as="form">
			<Form.Group>
				<Caption as="label" for="name">
					Your Name
				</Caption>
				<Form.Input
					name="name"
					type="text"
					placeholder="e.g. John Doe"
				/>
			</Form.Group>
		</Section>
	</React.Fragment>
);
